      "description": "## __task_pid_nr_ns(current, PIDTYPE_TGID, NULL)\n\n1. `ns = task_active_pid_ns(current);`: 名前空間を取得\n2. `nr = pid_nr_ns(rcu_dereference(*task_pid_ptr(current, PIDTYPE_TGID)), ns);`",
